{"tid":184181,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"男朋友話我唔應佢，佢都唔會唔開心","createTime":"2017-04-02T15:31:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-03T05:21:37.000Z","uid":28614,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6c9a31bab245cb25ab817f557a082644f1056198","tid":184181,"uid":28614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T15:31:44.000Z","msg":"同男朋友拍左差唔多四個月拖<br />\n已經當左佢係終身伴侶<br />\n最重要既處都比左佢<br />\n之前已經有個問題<br />\n就係我唔回佢一陣，佢就會好唔開心(當然我都係<br />\n我自問已經一得閒就回佢<br />\n有時做緊野番緊工，真係手機都禁唔到<br />\n前排去旅行，日日行程都好緊湊<br />\n7點起2,3點先訓<br />\n我認有忽略左佢，最長隔1,2個鐘先回到佢<br />\n到依家番番黎香港chur完<br />\n掛住佢想見佢多d傾番多d計既時候<br />\n佢話已經習慣左我唔理佢<br />\n佢話:你唔應我，我都唔會唔開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我係到諗。。姐係我消失左。。你都唔care?<br />\n明明我都唔係刻意唔理佢<br />\n依家揾佢，佢都好耐先回我<br />\n比我感覺係。。已經唔再在乎我<br />\n但其實我心一直冇變<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n相處好難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 自己冇意識犯錯<br />\n到依家自己又受番<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好矛盾好辛苦<br />\n我可以點做，求屌醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5e4a81dbc4f477955a8afa6f269cc0dc49d2403","tid":184181,"uid":828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T15:33:49.000Z","msg":"補返個處先"},{"pid":"9a6aff2b750921cab123cb8d697112f6c2f2a530","tid":184181,"uid":16685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T15:35:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>補返個處先</blockquote><br />\n快我一步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3dff1549f41d30019845e6a5754ce102a6de4492","tid":184181,"uid":101760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T15:35:52.000Z","msg":"一齊之前協議咗嘅規矩就最好做足<br />\n如果唔係真係你點對佢佢就點對你<br />\n何況係d收過重傷嘅人<br />\n同佢講清楚表達你嘅難處<br />\n再協議點做<br />\n安全感 就係 應承左就履行<br />\n好自為之啦樓主"},{"pid":"8b3512c438fded2ff29cdf28b4555d8523293ea5","tid":184181,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T15:36:34.000Z","msg":"4個月。終身<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd4bd9fc54b29a41dda450d1e5d6fe31f9e62745","tid":184181,"uid":23706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T15:37:01.000Z","msg":"帶個姊妹黎 比多個處佢"},{"pid":"d8d3896d54db5545c38fa919ad5ea0b04f3f79d4","tid":184181,"uid":86856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T15:37:03.000Z","msg":"我同你一樣阿絲打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n去完旅行返黎男朋友話我變左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n跟住又係話我去旅行個陣唔係點理佢<br />\n我已經解釋左因為我無咩點玩電話<br />\n而家都唔知點好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d0fc52577918640bc5bf1f2ed7ca32beb2a1ca8","tid":184181,"uid":75694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T15:37:29.000Z","msg":"拍得四個月拖就又呢樣嗰樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c2e46021f4b7d086360f416dc98496913dc6772","tid":184181,"uid":28614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T15:37:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>補返個處先</blockquote><br />\n之前拍左幾次拖，都冇比<br />\n覺得個處一定要係比老公<br />\n但係佢一開始比到信心同安全感我<br />\n會同我行落去唔會掉低我<br />\n所以我信左佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73aafb7232e0ac71bc7d229290b36bde351fa31c","tid":184181,"uid":28614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T15:39:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一齊之前協議咗嘅規矩就最好做足<br />\n如果唔係真係你點對佢佢就點對你<br />\n何況係d收過重傷嘅人<br />\n同佢講清楚表達你嘅難處<br />\n再協議點做<br />\n安全感 就係 應承左就履行<br />\n好自為之啦樓主</blockquote><br />\n收到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0e482067ab3a19832580fbb73b571d54c46a17b","tid":184181,"uid":28614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T15:39:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我同你一樣阿絲打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n去完旅行返黎男朋友話我變左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n跟住又係話我去旅行個陣唔係點理佢<br />\n我已經解釋左因為我無咩點玩電話<br />\n而家都唔知點好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 絲打<br />\n有人明我，我依家唔識點處理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e08a38bad6b819e84eba0f0ed26a4d6096e7ab4c","tid":184181,"uid":28614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T15:42:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>拍得四個月拖就又呢樣嗰樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n以前拍過一次拖，已經受重傷<br />\n諗住唔會再拍拖<br />\n但佢比到信心我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以我決定，如果分左手<br />\n我終身不嫁，或者去自殺<br />\n早已經唔想做人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de4200bb197d226960db65e620a9f5162a453631","tid":184181,"uid":828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T15:42:33.000Z","msg":"佢咁做一係就已經唔鍾意你<br />\n但又唔想做衰人 所以就推個波俾你 話你唔理佢<br />\n一係就發脾氣扭計 咁你咪多d搵佢 一係就送野俾佢氹佢囉"},{"pid":"f08efb11564b0b5bc974e6344e2bef003c39cf2c","tid":184181,"uid":78416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T15:43:00.000Z","msg":"返工要用whatsapp同PR傾野<br />\n佢話我成日上線 /唔係第一個覆佢 etc<br />\n依家有咩佢就大大聲話: 吓?我學你咋/你都係咁㗎咋之前 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0de15a2712cae0bfcdf58edef0b6d11596a66c69","tid":184181,"uid":62506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T15:44:17.000Z","msg":"第一，飛如佢<br />\n<br />\n第二，補返個處(視乎需要)"},{"pid":"34ca1a3c246ec12ebe8a1db405dfb16141b39d06","tid":184181,"uid":62506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T15:45:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>第一，飛<span style=\"color: red;\">左</span>佢<br />\n<br />\n第二，補返個處(視乎需要)</blockquote>"},{"pid":"fc86d2a58dd4346ba3a6bcd42f32700c2e666bd4","tid":184181,"uid":53794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T15:45:35.000Z","msg":"無lu<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  樓主個處就咁無咗 <br />\n不過有4個月歡樂時光都值啦"},{"pid":"6a0561cea1523652f5f591a426104af2985e461a","tid":184181,"uid":28614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T15:45:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢咁做一係就已經唔鍾意你<br />\n但又唔想做衰人 所以就推個波俾你 話你唔理佢<br />\n一係就發脾氣扭計 咁你咪多d搵佢 一係就送野俾佢氹佢囉</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我就係依家成日揾佢<br />\n佢都冇乜反應<br />\n好多野，我自己都唔捨得買比自己<br />\n都買比佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好似都氹唔到"},{"pid":"84980a1de7cc42d008c48a0552b522ae5b1bdcda","tid":184181,"uid":79353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T15:48:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>佢咁做一係就已經唔鍾意你<br />\n但又唔想做衰人 所以就推個波俾你 話你唔理佢<br />\n一係就發脾氣扭計 咁你咪多d搵佢 一係就送野俾佢氹佢囉</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我就係依家成日揾佢<br />\n佢都冇乜反應<br />\n好多野，我自己都唔捨得買比自己<br />\n都買比佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好似都氹唔到</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n人性本賤 我相信如此論調"},{"pid":"5b824cda78bbdf12402a94fb02e3350ba3ba367e","tid":184181,"uid":28614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T15:49:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>無lu<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  樓主個處就咁無咗 <br />\n不過有4個月歡樂時光都值啦</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我一直好自愛<br />\n我冇濫交，冇隨便同人搞<br />\n我咁大個人依家先比第一次<br />\n因為我信任佢，會同我走落去<br />\n點解要講到我好似雞咁"},{"pid":"8d8422942bb4c30ebe610d43187f51170ec643e2","tid":184181,"uid":79353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T15:51:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>無lu<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  樓主個處就咁無咗 <br />\n不過有4個月歡樂時光都值啦</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我一直好自愛<br />\n我冇濫交，冇隨便同人搞<br />\n我咁大個人依家先比第一次<br />\n因為我信任佢，會同我走落去<br />\n點解要講到我好似雞咁</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n上網D人隱姓埋名把口特別賤<br />\n<br />\n一個唔該可能佢係你現實中識既人<br />\n<br />\n或者REPLY呢條友就係你果條仆街男朋友"},{"pid":"148838788ece45c10f68c1682c49f9434458a57c","tid":184181,"uid":75694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T15:51:18.000Z","msg":"正常最sweet嘅頭幾個月蜜月期 你都唔理佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢隻鑊點補呀"},{"pid":"09463d1f2a949fdabb17f67ba3b14444b55211fd","tid":184181,"uid":79508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T16:00:25.000Z","msg":"樓主佢話習慣左姐<br />\n以我為例 我一開始一定朝早叫佢起身 夜晚講goodnight咁 有一whatsapp又秒回 咁行左咁耐 大家如果真係認定左大家 自然想投入返自己嘅生活 即係人地口中嘅老夫老妻 而且我認為訊息真係冇乜野 最緊要係見面嗰陣 你地會唔會冇野講 好淡咁<br />\n我同我條女拍左九個月拖 佢呀媽直程當我係仔咁 我地宜家仲係一個星期見兩三次 但係問心 whatsapp一定冇以前覆到咁 什至有時佢覆我 我打緊機 我會打完得閒先覆 問題係 我地感情純粹係唔需要再靠秒回黎維繫(當然訊息係要有嘅) 我地會好信得過對方 亦都唔洗下下依賴住對方<br />\n利申個人見解 拍過六次拖"},{"pid":"c5511a7e0eccf16cd22b4760cd5ae8a4f36d2d97","tid":184181,"uid":1732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T16:00:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>正常最sweet嘅頭幾個月蜜月期 你都唔理佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢隻鑊點補呀</blockquote><br />\n咪係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你覺得有問題就拎出黎同佢傾 自已係到煩又唔會解決到<br />\n我自已就受過重傷 亦都明白大家有難處 <br />\n<br />\n有時男人都要氹下架 老老豆豆 想人點對你就點樣去對人<br />\n你以前做錯 真係會改既咪話俾佢聽會改 再做俾佢睇囉<br />\n<br />\n唔好咁快就將拍拖固定係一個形式入面 就算做嘢忙 放假就搵啲共同興趣 一齊做啲開心既嘢 留多啲回憶俾大家<br />\n<br />\n一段長久既愛情係真係要俾心機經驗架 你當佢係終身對象就唔好咁快怕攰 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我好似代入咗個角色添<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"247e33afe3ee72e6c281a2f61fe8def3b406754b","tid":184181,"uid":28614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T16:01:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>無lu<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  樓主個處就咁無咗 <br />\n不過有4個月歡樂時光都值啦</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我一直好自愛<br />\n我冇濫交，冇隨便同人搞<br />\n我咁大個人依家先比第一次<br />\n因為我信任佢，會同我走落去<br />\n點解要講到我好似雞咁</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n上網D人隱姓埋名把口特別賤<br />\n<br />\n一個唔該可能佢係你現實中識既人<br />\n<br />\n或者REPLY呢條友就係你果條仆街男朋友</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 呢個世界咩都有。。我明"}]}